Subject: [PATCH] Revert "usb: cdc-wdm: close race between read and workqueue"
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 1607830dadeefc407e4956336d9fcd9e9defd810
